00:16:31,505 --> 00:16:33,547
He wanted to make sure that it was non-meaningful,

347
00:16:33,547 --> 00:16:37,991
so it was no familiarity with the content he was learning.

348
00:16:37,991 --> 00:16:39,432
And so he learned a chunk of them

