00:17:05,545 --> 00:17:10,146
But it means that when you learn something that you

361
00:17:10,146 --> 00:17:13,487
don't care about, that is not meaningful with no

362
00:17:13,487 --> 00:17:17,029
methodology of any kind, you're very likely to lose

