00:18:38,127 --> 00:18:42,110
and we want them to focus on where to find these ingredients,

391
00:18:42,110 --> 00:18:44,391
harvesting them, and then crafting the item.

392
00:18:44,391 --> 00:18:45,252
That's how we do it.

393
00:18:45,352 --> 00:18:47,214
what's important in the experience,

394
00:18:47,214 --> 00:18:49,337
not remembering the ingredients.

395
00:18:49,337 --> 00:18:53,563
So we allow for functionality where you pin the ingredients,

396
00:18:53,563 --> 00:18:56,487
you pin the recipe in your head.

397
00:18:56,487 --> 00:18:57,748
So you do not have to remember that.

398
00:18:59,353 --> 00:19:02,736
So it's important to keep that in mind,

399
00:19:02,736 --> 00:19:04,878
to remember that we don't remember well.

