00:20:32,797 --> 00:20:36,981
you don't know that they are happening and you're just focusing on other information,

429
00:20:36,981 --> 00:20:42,327
it's likely that you're not even going to realize that something's going on.

430
00:20:42,327 --> 00:20:45,290
And that's because our attention is scarce.

