00:27:09,968 --> 00:27:11,489
And then in the end,

568
00:27:11,829 --> 00:27:13,851
we have task creation.

569
00:27:13,851 --> 00:27:16,072
So there's always takeaways, and we're

570
00:27:16,072 --> 00:27:18,254
going to act upon several things.

571
00:27:18,254 --> 00:27:21,116
We discuss with the team, of course,

572
00:27:21,116 --> 00:27:24,939
to define what we're going to do, what we want to act upon.

573
00:27:24,939 --> 00:27:28,521
And that's really important to have that relationship.

