590
00:28:29,264 --> 00:28:32,429
is with the weak points in Fortnite.

591
00:28:33,182 --> 00:28:35,923
So you have weak points in Fortnite when you start

592
00:28:35,923 --> 00:28:37,605
destroying something.

593
00:28:37,605 --> 00:28:40,647
There's a little pop-up that tells you where to

594
00:28:40,647 --> 00:28:42,148
aim to go faster.

595
00:28:42,148 --> 00:28:45,190
And of course, the math and the system design is based off

596
00:28:45,190 --> 00:28:46,531
players using this.

597
00:28:46,531 --> 00:28:49,233
And so if players don't know about this and they don't use

598
00:28:49,233 --> 00:28:52,135
it, then of course, they're going to feel that the game is

599
00:28:52,135 --> 00:28:52,455
grindy.

600
00:28:52,455 --> 00:28:55,817
And at the beginning, the players were not seeing this

601
00:28:55,817 --> 00:28:56,498
little thing.

602
00:28:56,498 --> 00:28:58,239
They were just ignoring it.

