00:28:58,657 --> 00:29:01,077
And when I was asking what it is, they were like,

604
00:29:01,077 --> 00:29:02,458
I don't know.

605
00:29:02,458 --> 00:29:07,359
So we iterated on it, and the UI artists

606
00:29:07,359 --> 00:29:12,981
changed it to make it more popping out, standing out.

607
00:29:12,981 --> 00:29:16,082
And still the players were not using it.

608
00:29:16,082 --> 00:29:17,482
So we're like, what the hell?

609
00:29:17,482 --> 00:29:20,283
And when we were asking them what is this,

610
00:29:20,283 --> 00:29:23,684
players were saying, oh, this is where I'm targeting,

611
00:29:23,684 --> 00:29:26,005
this is telling me that I'm targeting this element.

612
00:29:26,682 --> 00:29:31,065
So in the end, what the designers did is they,

613
00:29:31,065 --> 00:29:35,149
in the PVE mode, at some point you're gonna unlock,

614
00:29:35,149 --> 00:29:38,551
you don't have that ability right away,

615
00:29:38,551 --> 00:29:40,973
you unlock it in the skill tree.

616
00:29:40,973 --> 00:29:44,436
So now it's an event, now it has meaning,

617
00:29:44,436 --> 00:29:47,078
and now players know there's something new.

618
00:29:47,078 --> 00:29:50,001
