631
00:30:23,828 --> 00:30:25,229
You're working with them

632
00:30:25,229 --> 00:30:27,090
and you're helping them solving the problems.

633
00:30:27,090 --> 00:30:29,872
And then you establish quick wins,

634
00:30:29,872 --> 00:30:31,853
you have a common language,

